code: 0
stdout:
project: fixture (sya)

schema:
- bug | open -> triage -> impl* -> verify* -> done! -> scrapped!
- decision | proposed -> accepted -> superseded! -> rejected!
- docs | todo -> writing* -> done!
- epic | open -> active* -> done! -> scrapped!
- feature: Пользовательская функциональность: через спеку и ревью, impl не начинается без утверждённой спеки | draft -> spec -> impl* -> review* -> done! -> scrapped!
- task | todo -> in_progress* -> done! -> scrapped!

relations:
- affects | reverse affected_by
- depends_on | reverse blocks | dag | blocking: Зависимость по работе: цель должна быть закрыта раньше начала/закрытия источника
- discovered_from | reverse discovered | dag
- duplicates | reverse duplicated_by
- relates | symmetric
- superseded_by | reverse supersedes

ready:
- f00001 [feature/draft/high] Build API
- d00001 [task/in_progress/normal] Dependency Task
- e00001 [epic/open/normal] Platform Epic

in-progress:
- d00001 [task/in_progress] @codex Dependency Task

memory:
- deploy-process: Deploys require green doctor
- streaming-api-uses-sse: Streaming API uses SSE
